<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span><strong><span>广东</span></strong></span><strong><span>、浙江、江苏、山东、上海；</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>城市购买力TOP5：</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong><span>上海、北京、杭州、深圳、</span></strong><span><strong><span>广州</span></strong></span></span></p>
